<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt_BR">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Locais Cadastrados</title>


  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.7.1/dist/leaflet.css"
    integrity="sha512-xodZBNTC5n17Xt2atTPuE1HxjVMSvLVW9ocqUKLsCC5CXdbqCmblAshOMAS6/keqq/sMZMZ19scR4PsZChSR7A=="
    crossorigin="" />

  <!-- Make sure you put this AFTER Leaflet's CSS -->
  <script src="https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.7.1/dist/leaflet.js"
    integrity="sha512-XQoYMqMTK8LvdxXYG3nZ448hOEQiglfqkJs1NOQV44cWnUrBc8PkAOcXy20w0vlaXaVUearIOBhiXZ5V3ynxwA=="
    crossorigin=""></script>

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/animations.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/page-orphanages.css" />


  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito:wght@400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>

<body>
  <div id="page-orphanages" style="background-color: #ff6961;">
    <p  style="background-color: #ff6961; margin: auto;">
      <a class="primary-button" onclick="hidemenu()" type="button" href="#">
        <img src="/images/plus.svg" alt="Menu">
      </a>
    </p>
    <aside id="headerItem" class="animate-right">

      <header>
        <h2>Escolha um local</h2>
        <p>São mostrados somente os fornecedores que, no momento da atualização, possuiam capacidade de atendimento</p>
        <p>Se você for um revendedor, e seu estabelecimento estiver desatualizado ou não cadastrado </p>
        <p>Entre em contato diretamente comigo</p>
        <p>
          <a href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send?l=pt_BR&phone=92981704683&text=Oi Lucas, gostaria de passar uma informação"
            target="_blank" class="primary-button" type="button">
            <img src="/images/whatsapp.svg" alt="Chamar no whatsapp" />
          </a>
          (92) 98170-4683
        </p>
      </header>
    </aside>

    <div id="mapid" class="animate-appear"></div>


    <div class="orphanages">
      {{#each locais}}
      <span hidden data-id="{{this.id}}" data-name="{{this.name}}" data-lat="{{this.lat}}"
        data-lng="{{this.lng}}"></span>

      {{/each}}
    </div>


    <!--
    <a href="/create-orphanage" class="create-orphanage" title="Cadastre um orfanato">
      <img src="/images/plus.svg" alt="Criar orfanato" />
    </a>
    -->
  </div>

  <script src="/scripts/page-orphanages.js"></script>
  <script>
    function hidemenu() {
      var x = document.getElementById("headerItem");
      if (x.style.display === "none") {
        x.style.display = "flex";
      } else {
        x.style.display = "none";
      }
    }
  </script>

</body>

</html>